15-yr-old Delhi girl found locked inside house for 2 yrs.
In a shocking incident, a 15-year-old girl was locked inside a house in east Delhi's Krishna Nagar for two years by her mother.The matter came to light after a neighbour, who suspected that something was not right, informed the Delhi Police, who raided the house and rescued the girl.The room in which the girl was kept was found to be full of garbage.Locals told the police that the woman, Krishna Ghosh, who is the mother of the victim, would visit the house in the evening only to bring food for the girl.